net.proteusframework.internet.http.resource

Interface WeightedHostname

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ResourceHostname
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WeightedHostnameImpl

    public interface WeightedHostname
extends ResourceHostname
    Hostname for serving a resource that weights itself. Use this in combination with a HostnameSelector that handles weighted hostnames.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
